  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n[@eth-optimism/watcher](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@eth-optimism/watcher) misses TS's type declarations (`d.ts` files). \r\n\r\nThey are specified in package.json (`types` field) but are not part of the final package uploaded to npm.\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\nProbably files in package.json should be changed from:\r\n\r\n```\r\n\"files\": [\r\n    \"build/**/*.js\"\r\n  ],\r\n```\r\n\r\nto:\r\n\r\n```\r\n\"files\": [\r\n    \"build/**/*.js\",\r\n\t \"build/**/*.ts\"\r\n  ],\r\n```",
